     <div type="dedication">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>TO SCOTLAND.</head>
   <l>BEhold the shaddow of thy Warrelike Sonne</l>
   <l>Great Mother, from whose Worthie-fertile Wombe</l>
   <l>So manie thousands haue tane birth, and wonnne</l>
   <l>An endlesse Fame abroad, and Name at home:</l>
   <l>Sharing the glorie of each Conquest great,</l>
   <l>And Victorie obtainde in brave defaite.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>LAWDER.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
